Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.91,0:03:43.22,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,話は聞いたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:43.90,def2,FUMIHIRO.,0,0,0,,I've heard the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.90,0:03:48.23,def2,FUMIHIRO.,0,0,0,,I called Ryosuke's cell,\Nbut it seems to be turned off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:45.92,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,涼介の携帯に掛けてみたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.98,0:03:47.48,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,電源がはいてなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:50.51,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,メッセージを残したけど返て来ないし
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.23,0:03:51.20,def2,FUMIHIRO.,0,0,0,,I left a message,\Nbut I haven't heard back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:53.01,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,大学の研究室にもいないって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:54.17,def2,FUMIHIRO.,0,0,0,,I've been told that he's not\Nin the college lab either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.07,0:03:57.05,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,涼介がFCを密かに改造していたとすれば
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:59.63,def2,FUMIHIRO.,0,0,0,,If Ryosuke secretly modified his FC,\NI'm sure he must have a reason for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:59.83,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対何か目的があるはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.85,0:04:04.92,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,FCのチューニングやメンテンナンスをずっと手がけてきたのは松本だからさ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.95,0:04:06.40,def2,FUMIHIRO.,0,0,0,,Matsumoto is the one who's been \Ntuning and maintaining the FC...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:10.46,def2,FUMIHIRO.,0,0,0,,...so I've tried calling him to find \Nout if he knows something, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:09.77,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,松本なら何か知ってるんじゃないかと思って電話してるんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:12.12,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こっちも連絡取れない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:12.79,def2,FUMIHIRO.,0,0,0,,{kocchi}...I can't reach him either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:14.74,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,二人揃って行方不明だなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:16.83,def2,FUMIHIRO.,0,0,0,,Something is definitely not\Nright with both of them missing.{ that both of them are missing.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:16.74,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どう考えても引っかかるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:19.12,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そういう事なら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.83,0:04:22.27,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,If that's the case, I'll just ignore this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:22.16,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この件は　あえて忘れる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:23.65,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,Huh ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:27.87,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,I mean, for the time being it's\Npointless for us to get upset over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.67,0:04:26.88,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ここで俺たちがジタバタしてるも始まらないって事だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:30.87,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうはいかないだろう　心配じゃないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:31.86,def2,FUMIHIRO.,0,0,0,,How could you not be ? \NAren't you worried ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:34.28,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,兄貴が動くからには相応の理由がある
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:35.28,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,My brother must have a \Nsignificant reason for doing this...{make his move...}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:37.96,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺達に黙って　単独で行動するのにもな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.28,0:04:38.00,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,...including {his action of}going solo behind our back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:42.53,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,昔からそうなんだ　史浩なら分かるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:43.00,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,He's always been been like this.{ from way back. }\NYou know that, don't you ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:45.20,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,{aniki}He always makes the right choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:44.84,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,兄貴のやることに間違いはない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:49.51,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,必ず何事も無かったのようにシレッと帰ってくる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.90,0:04:50.49,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,{kanarazu}He'll come back and {with fake}feign \Nignorance as if nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.44,0:04:52.03,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,信じて待っていればいいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:54.70,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,Just have faith in him and wait.\NThere's no point in worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.87,0:04:54.53,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,心配なんてしなくていい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.59,0:04:57.09,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな普段どおりのことをやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:57.65,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,{minna}Let's just act like we normally do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:05:01.49,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,What we should be doing now\Nis preparing for the final battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:04:59.48,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今俺達がやるべき事は
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:01.60,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,最終戦に向けての準備だろ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.91,0:05:05.46,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,兄貴がこの場にいたら絶対にそういうはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.98,0:05:05.70,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,That's what my brother\Nwould say if he were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.02,0:05:10.08,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,There's no need to worry\Nabout a remote{slim} possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:08.86,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もしもの事なんてありえない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.01,0:05:13.09,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,兄貴は日本一クレバーな公道ランナーだってことを
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:13.50,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,He's Japan's most ingenious{clever} street racer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:15.17,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,Don't forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.52,0:05:14.78,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,忘れるなって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:21.65,Karaoke Translation op,..TITLE..,0,0,0,,{\pos(701,455)}{\fscx108\fscy105\pos(615,467)}{\3c&H000000&}Grim Reaper
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:29.14,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,涼介さん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.40,0:05:30.26,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,Ryosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:33.06,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺はここで待ってます
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.40,0:05:35.02,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting here, so please\Npick me up when you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.59,0:05:35.13,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,終わったら拾いに来て下さい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:39.60,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は涼介さんの助手席で群馬に帰る予定ですから
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:40.65,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,I plan{planned} to return to Gunma\Nin your car's passenger seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:42.78,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それ以外の手段で帰るつもりはないです
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:43.21,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,I haven't thought about any other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:46.19,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,二日でも三日でもここで待ってます
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:46.00,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,Even if it takes several days, I'll be waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:51.73,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,例え雨を降っても　例え土砂降りの雨になっても
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.65,0:05:51.70,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,Even if it rains, to the point where I get soaked...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:55.36,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり　貴方が戻らなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:57.78,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,{tsumari}{I mean}In other words, if you\Ndon't return, I'll die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:57.94,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺もこの場所でのたれ死ぬ予定です
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:02.73,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前ならやり兼ねないな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:03.00,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,I can really see you doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:05.76,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,必ず戻る
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:06.90,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,I'll return no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.87,0:06:07.57,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:07.70,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.04,0:06:27.12,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,約束ですよ　涼介さん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:27.12,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}It's a promise, Ryosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:32.49,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Please come back safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:32.40,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,無事に戻ってきてください
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:41.07,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,白いFC
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.91,0:06:41.63,def2,.IKETANI.,0,0,0,,A white FC ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.57,0:06:42.77,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:42.90,def2,..KENJI..,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:46.72,def2,..KENJI..,0,0,0,,A guy saw it when he was\Nvisiting Akagi the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:46.17,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この間　赤城の方へ行った奴が見たって
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.65,0:06:50.36,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それって　高橋涼介が観瀑したってことか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.72,0:06:50.59,def2,.IKETANI.,0,0,0,,Do you mean Takahashi\NRyosuke is making a comeback ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:52.19,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなはずないっすよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:52.40,def2,.ITSUKI..,0,0,0,,There's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:54.68,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,コアなファンが真似してるだけじゃないっすか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:55.07,def2,.ITSUKI..,0,0,0,,It's probably a copy by a hardcore fan.{ could be a copy by a hardcore fan.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.92,0:06:56.91,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なら　まだいいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.07,0:06:56.80,def2,..KENJI..,0,0,0,,That could be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:07:01.23,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら　この前みたいに偽物が現れたとか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.76,0:07:01.66,def2,..KENJI..,0,0,0,,Remember those impersonators the other day ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.57,0:07:03.07,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それはないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:03.65,def2,.IKETANI.,0,0,0,,That's not likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:05.74,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,赤城は高橋涼介の地元なんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:05.90,def2,.IKETANI.,0,0,0,,Akagi is Takahashi Ryosuke's home ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:07.58,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,偽物なんてすぐにバレるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.90,def2,.IKETANI.,0,0,0,,Any impersonator would\Nget caught immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:09.19,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうっすよね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:09.13,def2,.ITSUKI..,0,0,0,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.30,0:07:13.55,def2,.IKETANI.,0,0,0,,Hey, did Takumi say anything ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.31,0:07:13.14,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なぁ　拓海は何も言ってなかったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.42,0:07:15.14,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何も聞いてないっすけど
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:15.10,def2,.ITSUKI..,0,0,0,,Not a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:17.66,def2,.ITSUKI..,0,0,0,,I'd better call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.36,0:07:17.90,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと電話してみます
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:21.57,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつこんまえみたいに親友差し置いてしかとしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.55,0:07:23.53,def2,.ITSUKI..,0,0,0,,If he ignores his best friend like he did the other day, I'll chew him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:23.57,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こんどこそ徹底的に取っちめてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:29.47,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,涼介さんが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.25,0:07:31.06,def2,.TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,Ryosuke did ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.02,0:07:33.67,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　そんな話全然聞いてないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:34.49,def2,.TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,No, I don't know anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:37.24,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,うん　単に似た車だったんじゃないかな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:38.24,def2,.TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,Maybe it's just a look-alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:39.33,def2,.TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,Okay, bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:39.37,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,うん　じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:43.68,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしたの　また偽物騒ぎ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:44.41,def2,..MIKA...,0,0,0,,What's wrong ?\NAnother impersonator ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:47.77,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ　いいや　別にそこまでは言ってないと思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:48.44,def2,.TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,Um, no, I don't think it's that serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.33,0:07:54.32,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,でも今になって見れば　あの偽物に感謝しなくちゃね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.45,0:07:54.50,def2,..MIKA...,0,0,0,,But come to think of it, we have\Nto thank those impersonators.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:08:00.70,def2,..MIKA...,0,0,0,,After all, I met you because of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:58.45,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だって　あの二人のおかげで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.55,0:08:00.59,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こうして拓海君に出会えたんだもの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:02.75,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:02.70,def2,.TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.65,0:08:06.60,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ね　拓海くん　また二人でどうか行こうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.82,0:08:07.30,def2,..MIKA...,0,0,0,,Hey, Takumi, why don't we go\Nsomewhere together again ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:09.48,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,海は行ったから　今度は山かな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:09.40,def2,..MIKA...,0,0,0,,{umi}We've been to the beach,\Nso how about the mountains ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:34.73,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,危険過ぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:34.80,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}This is way too risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:41.12,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I've never seen such a high-speed \Ndownhill stage like this anywhere.{elsewhere}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:38.32,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これほどの超高速ダウンヒルステージは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:40.13,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,他では見たことがない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:42.70,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,コースを知っている地元を相手に
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:45.35,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}It's really disadvantageous to be in\Nthe lead position against a local.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:44.70,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,先行はあまりにも不利だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:47.79,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ブランクがある上に
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:51.60,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}He hasn't had time to become familiar\Nwith the renewed FC after his hiatus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:51.53,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,リニューアルしたFCに対応するだけの時間も無かった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:55.97,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,けど　ここまで来たらもう信じるしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:09:01.10,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{But all I can do now is believe in his\Nsuperb driving sense as Akagi's White Comet.}But all I can do now is believe in the super driving\Nsense from his days as Akagi's White Comet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.71,0:08:58.99,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,赤城の白い彗星と呼ばれていた頃の
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:03.44,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,冴え渡っていたドライビングセンスを　涼介さん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:03.58,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Ryosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.84,0:09:16.93,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,三年前かな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:17.70,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,Three years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:18.30,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,Eh ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:23.75,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,...{I fell in love with a woman.}I fell in love with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.61,0:09:22.55,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺はある人を好きになったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:26.66,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,その人は大学の一年先輩で
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:30.74,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,She was my senior by one year at college,\Nand a type of person I hadn't met before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:30.78,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それまではあまり出会ったことはないタイプの人だった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:36.91,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,自由奔放で　大人と子供が同居していて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:37.00,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,Free-spirited, half childish, half mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:44.83,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,強いくせにもろい　矛盾だらけの人だったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:45.73,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{tsuyoi}Sometimes strong-willed, but sometimes weak, a person with lots of contradictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:56.51,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,でも俺は　そんな所に引かれたのかもな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.06,0:09:57.70,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,But that's probably why I was attracted to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:09:59.47,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,自分でもコントロール出来ないくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:10:01.19,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,I lost my head over her to the \Nextent that I couldn't control myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:01.02,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,のぼせ上がっていたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:06.56,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,意外かもな　俺のそんな所は
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:06.50,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,It's out of character for me, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:15.88,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,I haven't told anyone about this, but can \Nyou bear with my little story, Matsumoto ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:12.19,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この事は　今まで誰にも話した事は無かったんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.18,0:10:15.92,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,少しだけ聞いてもらえるか　松本
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.69,0:10:44.04,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,旋回能力は互角か
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:47.70,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Cornering potential is equal, but my \Ncar has significantly greater power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.90,0:10:46.98,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,パワーは明らかにこっちが上だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:52.71,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,制動に関しては　軽い分向こうに利がある
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.32,0:10:53.65,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}As for braking, his car has the\Nadvantage because of the lighter weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.55,0:10:57.09,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,終盤に行けば行くほどそれは顕著なものになっていくだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:57.15,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{shuban}It will become more apparent\Ntoward the end of the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:03.73,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だが　俺にとっては好都合だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:03.89,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}But that works fine for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:10.15,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,止まれないなら　不可抗力としてぶつけるだけのこと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:11.00,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}If I can't stop, I won't be able to\Navoid slamming my car into his.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:23.04,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負は一本　見事に逃げきれれば　お前の勝ちだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.33,0:11:23.20,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}There will only be one round.{You'll have only one race.}\NIf you manage to get away, you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:28.33,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,逃がさないだな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.90,0:11:28.65,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}But I won't let you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.39,0:11:37.36,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,涼介君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.52,0:11:37.59,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}Ryosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:11:58.97,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,自分が何のために生まれてきたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:59.65,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,Why do you think you were born ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:04.51,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,考えたこと有る　涼介君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.35,0:12:04.45,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,Have you ever thought about it, Ryosuke ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:13.91,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,また出た　香織さんの禅問答が
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:14.20,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,There you go again. \NAnother philosophical question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.06,0:12:16.34,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,はぐらかなさないで答えてみなさいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.20,0:12:17.10,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,Don't dodge my question, try to answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:19.58,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,自分が本当にやりたいってことってなんなの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:19.80,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,What do you really want to do ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:30.23,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,親の跡を継ぐことがホントにしたいこと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:31.45,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,Do you really want to succeed your parents ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:35.92,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,君は本当に医者何かに成りたくてうちの大学にいるの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:35.93,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,Are you attending college because\Nyou actually want to become a doctor ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:42.65,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなのは恵まれてるとは言えないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:43.45,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,You can't be happy with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.38,0:12:46.87,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,寧ろ不幸よ　選択の自由のない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:48.14,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,It's rather sad{unhappy} if you can't \Nchoose what to do with your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.96,0:12:48.33,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,つまんない人生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.55,0:12:52.09,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,痛いとこ着くね　香織さん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:52.15,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,You're hitting a sore spot, Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:54.66,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,君の幸せってなに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:56.34,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,What makes you happy ?{is your happiness ?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.23,0:12:58.16,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,本当の幸せってなに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.34,0:12:58.50,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,What makes you truly happy ?{is your true happiness ?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.99,0:13:01.70,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,Don't you have a dream ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.15,0:13:01.28,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,夢はないの
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:04.65,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,涼介君の夢ってなに
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:05.01,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}What is your dream, Ryosuke ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:32.65,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.15,0:13:34.00,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,Any news ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:36.97,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,確認しました　死神のR３２です
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:37.20,def2,...MAN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}I spotted the Grim Reaper's R32.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:41.70,def2,...MAN...,0,0,0,,It'll pass by your location,\Nchasing a white car at high speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:41.60,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,白い車を追って　猛スピードでもうすぐそこを通過します
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.57,0:13:44.99,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,くれぐれも気をつけてください　池田さん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:45.50,def2,...MAN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}Please be very careful, Ikeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:46.21,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:46.20,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.90,0:14:20.43,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ついに捕捉したぜ　死神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.05,0:14:20.28,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I've finally got you, Grim Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:44.94,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,スパイラルは箱根の自警団的役割を自負しているチームだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.74,0:14:46.02,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Team Spiral is proud to be the\Nneighborhood watch of Hakone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:49.14,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,峠のルールを壊す存在には断じて許さん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.02,0:14:49.50,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}We won't forgive anyone who breaks\Nthe rules of the mountain pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:52.32,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたの狼藉も今日限りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:52.41,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Your insolence ends today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.43,0:14:59.37,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それにしても　まえを行く白いFCは何者だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:59.34,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Anyway, who's driving that white FC ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:05.67,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あの死神を相手に先行のポジションとはまた豪胆だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.44,0:15:06.60,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}How reckless of you to take the lead\Nposition against the Grim Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:10.72,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ者ではない　まさか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:08.80,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}He must have nerves of steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.15,0:15:11.70,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Could that be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:13.26,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}...him ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:13.07,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あの男か
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:23.04,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,涼介君　君に話してないことが有るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.15,0:15:23.09,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,Ryosuke, there's something I haven't told you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:46.44,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,私ね　親が決めた婚約者がいるの
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:46.35,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,I have a fiancé chosen by my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:51.84,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,後何年かしたらその人と結婚するんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:51.52,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,I'll have to marry him in a few years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:02.34,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,つまんないジョックだよね　香織さん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:02.20,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,That's a bad joke, Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:10.20,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,Do you really want to \Nfollow your parents' wishes ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:09.31,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,親の意思に従うことが　ホントに貴方のしたいことなの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:12.87,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなの全然貴方らしくないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.20,0:16:13.28,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,That's not like you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:17.18,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,君はホントの私を知らないだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.02,0:16:17.19,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,You just don't know the true me.{my true self.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:22.99,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なら　これから知ればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:23.00,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,Then I'll begin to discover it from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:27.54,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,I'm not going to give you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:27.72,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は　香織さんを諦めるつもりはないから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.76,0:16:29.39,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だめよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:30.02,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:35.89,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,諦めて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.00,0:16:37.27,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,Please give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.01,0:16:46.85,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なにが　香織さんを泣かすの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:47.01,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,Why are you crying ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:54.05,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は　なにがあっても　香織さんを守るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.92,0:16:54.23,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,I'll protect you no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.83,0:17:10.34,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした涼介
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.14,0:17:11.12,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}What's wrong, Ryosuke ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.94,0:17:14.10,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,コーナーの進入にわずかだが迷いが見えるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.12,0:17:15.02,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I see a slight hesitation in your corner entries.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:17.02,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,超高速ステージが怖いか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.02,0:17:17.55,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Are you scared of this\Nsuper high-speed stage ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:19.82,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Or is it because of your hiatus ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.59,0:17:19.35,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それともブランクのせいか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:27.41,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,甘いぜ涼介　寝ぼけてるんなら目を覚ませ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:25.45,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}You're so naive, Ryosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.45,0:17:27.32,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}If you're spacing out, I'll wake you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:32.50,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}He did it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.97,0:17:32.61,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,早速やりやがった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:37.32,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ターンイン直後の安定期に入る直前にあれをやられるのが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:40.34,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Rear wheel drive cars are defenseless against that kind\Nof push right after the turn-in when the car is unstable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:39.32,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,後輪駆動には一番辛い
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:42.82,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,死神は確信犯でそこをついてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.34,0:17:43.00,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}The Grim Reaper did it on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.70,0:17:45.00,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Please recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.81,0:17:44.91,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,立ち直ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:17:59.52,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,うまい　見事だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.83,0:17:59.65,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Wow, that was incredible.{'s fantastic.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:04.33,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}That's more like it.\NThat was my way of saying "Hi."{greeting.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.42,0:18:01.84,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうでなくちゃな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:04.11,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなのはあいさつ代わりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.64,0:18:17.71,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,コントロールできる　いい仕上がりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:16.55,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I can control the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:20.75,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}It's well tuned, as always, Matsumoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:20.18,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,さすがだな　松本
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.63,0:18:21.49,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これなら行ける
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:26.65,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{korenara}Now I know I can push myself\Nto the limit without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.26,0:18:26.10,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,心おきなく　ぎりぎりの領域へ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.28,0:18:30.24,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もう一発　次はきついぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:30.07,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Here comes the next one. It'll be harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.52,0:18:38.47,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,違う　今までと明らかに違う
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.69,0:18:39.20,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}The Grim Reaper is acting\Ndifferently from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:41.12,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}He's seriously trying to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.28,0:18:40.79,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,死神は本気で
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:52.00,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,外した
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.35,0:18:52.25,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}He missed ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:55.97,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あの死神が本気で当てに行ってかわされた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:56.11,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}The Grim Reaper's serious \Nattempt to crash was dodged.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.52,0:18:59.32,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんたるつっこみ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.73,0:18:59.81,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}What incredible acceleration.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.56,0:19:02.31,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もう間違いない　あのFCは
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.81,0:19:03.20,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{mou}There's no more doubt about that FC.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.18,0:19:06.90,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,北関東最強と言われた　カリスマの復活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:06.93,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{mou}The charismatic driver, who was once\Nthe best in northern Kanto, has returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.28,0:19:10.37,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,一体なにが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.40,0:19:11.00,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}What made him do that ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:17.62,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,涼介
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:17.83,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Ryosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:30.33,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なにが起こっているんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:30.50,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}What's going on ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.13,0:19:35.02,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,死神が変だ　あからさまに殺気を漲らせている
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:35.00,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}The Grim Reaper is acting strange,\Nshowing true{noticeably} hostile intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:37.68,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それを受けるあの男も
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.10,0:19:41.00,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}The other guy is well aware of it,\Nbut he isn't even trying to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.68,0:19:40.31,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それが分かっていながら離脱しようともしない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.92,0:19:44.08,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これはだたのバトルじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:44.20,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}This is no ordinary battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:48.22,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}It looks like I ran into\Nan extraordinary situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.97,0:19:48.28,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺はとんでもない場面に出くわしてしまったようだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.93,0:19:52.66,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,さすがだな　涼介
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:56.00,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Just like you, Ryosuke.\NYour earlier hesitation is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.28,0:19:55.55,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,先まであった躊躇が消えた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.77,0:19:58.82,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,素晴らしい順応力だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:19:59.50,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}You've got incredible adaptability.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:02.48,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}You're a much better \Ndriver than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:02.14,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は想像以上のドライバーだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.55,0:20:12.45,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,香織　近くに来て　見ているんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.72,0:20:12.50,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Are you nearby, Kaori, watching us ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.64,0:20:16.51,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,このバトルお前に捧げる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.70,0:20:16.70,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I dedicate this battle to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:22.08,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は　今夜この場所で死んでも悔いはない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:22.80,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Even if I die here tonight, I won't regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.73,0:20:24.38,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なにも怖くないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:24.20,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I'm not afraid of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:53.10,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ごめんなさい　北条さん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:54.65,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Hojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:56.37,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,I can't marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:56.16,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,結婚はできません
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.98,0:21:03.71,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,待ってくれ　それはないぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.10,0:21:06.51,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,Hold on, that's so abrupt. Tell me why.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.33,0:21:07.73,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,訳を言ってくれ　親が決めたからとか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.51,0:21:09.80,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,This has nothing to do with\Nour parents' arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.89,0:21:09.36,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そういう事じゃないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.64,0:21:12.36,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,分かってくれ　香織
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.73,0:21:16.22,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,Don't you know that I love you\Nfrom the bottom of my heart ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.86,0:21:16.21,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺はもう心の底からお前が好きだということを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:53.78,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,恐ろしいぜ　なんというテンションの高さだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:51.98,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}This is scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.98,0:21:54.35,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Their tension is off the scale.{s are so high.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:21:56.17,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,二人の間に割って入る所か
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.35,0:21:58.00,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I'm having a hard time keeping up with them, \Nmuch less cutting in between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:57.93,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ついて行くだけでも苦しい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.62,0:22:02.19,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それにしても高橋涼介
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:03.02,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Besides, that Takahashi Ryosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.69,0:22:07.83,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,理論派と聞いていたが　それは絶対に違う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.90,0:22:08.69,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I heard he was the logical type, but that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.51,0:22:11.38,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,天才タイプでしかこんな芸当は出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.69,0:22:11.84,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Only a genius could pull off this kind of driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:15.24,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,地元ではない走り屋がこれほどのペスを作れるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.84,0:22:16.60,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{jimoto}It's almost a miracle for a \Nnon-local to maintain this high pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.36,0:22:16.82,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ほとんど奇跡だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.02,0:22:25.64,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}This course is so unique that even the\Nlocals don't push themselves to the limit...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.17,0:22:20.65,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それほどそこは特別なコースなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.11,0:22:24.68,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,地元でも下りを限界まで攻めることはまずしない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:27.99,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,命がいくつあっても足りないからな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.64,0:22:27.91,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{inochi}...because you only have one life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.32,0:22:44.82,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,速い　芸術的なロータリー使いだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.44,0:22:42.70,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}So fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.70,0:22:46.09,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}His handling of the rotary\Nengine is almost an art.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:50.58,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,天才の感覚とクレーバー過ぎる頭脳が両立しているというわけか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:50.70,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{He has the sense of genius and a clever mind.}{brain.}  So, even being known as the logical type, it's because he\Nhas both the sense of a genius and an all-too-clever mind ?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.16,0:22:55.68,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それが理論派高橋涼介の真実だ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.20,0:22:55.70,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}That's the true nature of Takahashi Ryosuke.{ \Nwho's known as the logical type.}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.23,0:23:05.15,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だが死神のホントの恐ろしさは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.39,0:23:08.43,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}But the Grim Reaper will show his\Ntruly frightening nature up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.11,0:23:08.28,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これから先が本番なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.22,0:23:42.02,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,涼介君
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.40,0:23:42.82,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,Ryosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.57,0:23:47.32,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,君って不思議な人だね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.60,0:23:47.30,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,You're a mysterious person.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.89,0:23:53.97,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,年下のくせに落ち着いてて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.90,0:23:57.20,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,You're younger than me, but more \Ncomposed, which irritates me a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.68,0:23:56.62,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それがちょっとシャクに触るけど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.20,0:24:01.70,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,But you're always honest, \Nkind and strong-minded...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.35,0:24:00.50,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いつも誠実で優しくて　心が強い
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.37,0:24:06.04,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,きっと君は女の子を幸せにするんだろうね
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.55,0:24:06.17,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,...the type of person who\Ncan make a woman happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.83,0:24:11.15,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,私でいいの
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.02,0:24:13.80,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if I can be the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.48,0:24:13.57,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,自信ないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.10,0:24:19.80,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,Maybe I don't deserve your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.17,0:24:19.30,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,君に思われる資格　ないかも
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.69,0:24:27.48,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ずっと側にいられたら
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.96,0:24:27.65,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,I wish I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.67,0:24:42.59,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,君の側にいられたらいいの
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.80,0:24:43.30,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,...be by your side forever.
